Depende do que tem pra oferecer.

545
00:48:00,083 --> 00:48:01,439
Tudo.

546
00:48:01,440 --> 00:48:02,990
Tudo?

547
00:48:14,684 --> 00:48:17,083
Sim, tudo.

548
00:48:30,715 --> 00:48:33,947
